---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---
<MainLayout title="Cybersecurity | Blue Cap IT — Coro Partner" description="Blue Cap IT partners with Coro to deliver all-in-one cybersecurity for small and mid-sized businesses. Endpoint protection, email security, cloud app security, network protection, and more — one platform, one agent.">
  <div class="inner-hero">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="crumbs"><a href="index.html">Home</a> <span>/</span> Cybersecurity</div>
      <div class="section-label">Coro Partner</div>
      <h1>Cybersecurity <span class="grad">Made Simple</span></h1>
      <p class="section-sub">Blue Cap IT partners with Coro to bring enterprise-grade cybersecurity to small and mid-sized businesses — without the complexity. One platform. One agent. Complete protection.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- WHY CORO -->
  <section>
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="why-grid">
        <div>
          <div class="section-label">Why Coro</div>
          <h2>All-in-One Cybersecurity.<br/><span class="grad">Built for Your Business.</span></h2>
          <p class="section-sub">Most cybersecurity solutions were built for large enterprises with dedicated security teams. Coro was purpose-built for businesses like yours — powerful protection that doesn't require a team of specialists to manage.</p>
          <p class="section-sub" style="margin-top:1rem;">As a Coro Partner, Blue Cap IT deploys, configures, and manages Coro's platform for you — so you get complete cybersecurity coverage with zero added complexity.</p>
          <div style="margin-top:2rem;display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
            <a href="contact.html" class="btn-primary">Get Protected</a>
            <a href="tel:4108584031" class="btn-ghost">Call (410) 858-4031</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <ul class="why-list">
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon"><Icon name="lucide:shield" /></div>
            <div><h4>Complete Coverage</h4><p>Email, endpoints, cloud apps, network, and data — all protected from a single platform. No gaps, no bolt-on tools.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon"><Icon name="lucide:bot" /></div>
            <div><h4>AI-Powered Automation</h4><p>Coro's AI engine automatically detects and resolves threats — handling the vast majority of security events without manual intervention.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon"><Icon name="lucide:zap" /></div>
            <div><h4>Simple to Deploy</h4><p>One lightweight agent, one dashboard, one platform. No complex integrations or multi-vendor headaches.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon"><Icon name="lucide:trending-up" /></div>
            <div><h4>Scales With You</h4><p>Modular design lets you activate only the protection modules you need today — and add more as your business grows.</p></div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CORO MODULES -->
  <section style="background:var(--surface);">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div style="text-align:center;max-width:640px;margin:0 auto 2rem;">
        <div class="section-label">Coro Security Modules</div>
        <h2>One Platform.<br/><span class="grad">Total Protection.</span></h2>
        <p class="section-sub" style="margin:0.8rem auto 0;text-align:center;">Coro combines the security tools you'd normally buy separately into one unified, AI-driven platform.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="products-grid">
        <a href="coro-endpoint.html" class="product-card" style="text-decoration:none;color:inherit;">
          <div class="pcard-icon"><Icon name="lucide:laptop" /></div>
          <h3>Endpoint Protection</h3>
          <p>Next-gen antivirus and EDR (Endpoint Detection &amp; Response) for every device. Detects malware, ransomware, and advanced threats — then automatically contains and remediates them.</p>
          <span class="pcard-arrow">Learn more →</span>
        </a>
        <a href="coro-email.html" class="product-card" style="text-decoration:none;color:inherit;">
          <div class="pcard-icon"><Icon name="lucide:mail" /></div>
          <h3>Email Security</h3>
          <p>Blocks phishing, business email compromise, malware attachments, and spam before they reach your inbox. Works with Microsoft 365 and Google Workspace.</p>
          <span class="pcard-arrow">Learn more →</span>
        </a>
        <a href="coro-cloud.html" class="product-card" style="text-decoration:none;color:inherit;">
          <div class="pcard-icon"><Icon name="lucide:cloud" /></div>
          <h3>Cloud App Security</h3>
          <p>Monitors and protects your cloud applications — Microsoft 365, Google Workspace, Slack, Salesforce, and more. Detects unauthorized access, data leaks, and suspicious activity.</p>
          <span class="pcard-arrow">Learn more →</span>
        </a>
        <a href="coro-network.html" class="product-card" style="text-decoration:none;color:inherit;">
          <div class="pcard-icon"><Icon name="lucide:globe" /></div>
          <h3>Network Security</h3>
          <p>Zero Trust Network Access (ZTNA), VPN, firewall, and DNS filtering. Control who can access your network and what they can reach — from anywhere.</p>
          <span class="pcard-arrow">Learn more →</span>
        </a>
        <a href="coro-data.html" class="product-card" style="text-decoration:none;color:inherit;">
          <div class="pcard-icon"><Icon name="lucide:folder-lock" /></div>
          <h3>Data Governance</h3>
          <p>Discover, classify, and protect sensitive data across your organization. Enforce policies to prevent data loss and maintain compliance with industry regulations.</p>
          <span class="pcard-arrow">Learn more →</span>
        </a>
        <a href="coro-training.html" class="product-card" style="text-decoration:none;color:inherit;">
          <div class="pcard-icon"><Icon name="lucide:graduation-cap" /></div>
          <h3>Security Awareness Training</h3>
          <p>Educate your employees with engaging security training and simulated phishing campaigns. Turn your team from a vulnerability into your first line of defense.</p>
          <span class="pcard-arrow">Learn more →</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
  <section>
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div style="text-align:center;max-width:640px;margin:0 auto 2rem;">
        <div class="section-label">How It Works</div>
        <h2>Getting Started Is <span class="grad">Easy</span></h2>
      </div>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:1.5rem;max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;">
        <div class="spec-card" style="text-align:center;padding:2rem 1.2rem;">
          <div style="font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--elec);margin-bottom:0.7rem;font-family:'Sora',sans-serif;line-height:1;">1</div>
          <div style="font-family:'Sora',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:0.95rem;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Free Assessment</div>
          <div style="font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--text-muted);">We evaluate your current security posture and identify gaps in your protection.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="spec-card" style="text-align:center;padding:2rem 1.2rem;">
          <div style="font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--elec);margin-bottom:0.7rem;font-family:'Sora',sans-serif;line-height:1;">2</div>
          <div style="font-family:'Sora',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:0.95rem;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Custom Plan</div>
          <div style="font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--text-muted);">We recommend the right Coro modules for your business needs and budget.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="spec-card" style="text-align:center;padding:2rem 1.2rem;">
          <div style="font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--elec);margin-bottom:0.7rem;font-family:'Sora',sans-serif;line-height:1;">3</div>
          <div style="font-family:'Sora',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:0.95rem;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Deploy &amp; Protect</div>
          <div style="font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--text-muted);">We deploy the Coro agent, configure your policies, and start protecting your business — typically in under a day.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PARTNERSHIP -->
  <section style="background:var(--surface);">
    <div class="section-inner" style="text-align:center;max-width:700px;margin:0 auto;">
      <div class="section-label">Our Partnership</div>
      <h2>Official <span class="grad">Coro Partner</span></h2>
      <p class="section-sub" style="text-align:center;margin:0.8rem auto 1.5rem;">Coro is purpose-built cybersecurity for small and mid-sized businesses. Blue Cap IT is proud to be an official Coro Partner — bringing enterprise-grade cyber protection to businesses that need it most.</p>
      <img src="/Coro/coro-logo-wide-indigo.png" alt="Coro" style="height:50px;width:auto;margin:0 auto 2rem;display:block;"/>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(160px,1fr));gap:1.2rem;max-width:700px;margin:0 auto;">
        <div class="spec-card" style="text-align:center;padding:1.8rem 1rem;"><div style="font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:0.7rem;color:var(--elec);"><Icon name="lucide:shield" /></div><div style="font-family:'Sora',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:0.9rem;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:0.3rem;">Coro Partner</div><div style="font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--text-muted);">Authorized Coro Reseller</div></div>
        <div class="spec-card" style="text-align:center;padding:1.8rem 1rem;"><div style="font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:0.7rem;color:var(--elec);"><Icon name="lucide:bot" /></div><div style="font-family:'Sora',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:0.9rem;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:0.3rem;">AI-Driven</div><div style="font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--text-muted);">Automated Threat Resolution</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <div class="cta-band">
    <div class="section-label">Let's Talk Cybersecurity</div>
    <h2>Protect Your Business<br/><span class="grad">with Blue Cap IT + Coro</span></h2>
    <p>Contact us for a free cybersecurity assessment. We'll evaluate your current security posture and show you how Coro can close the gaps — with simple, transparent pricing.</p>
    <div class="btn-group">
      <a href="contact.html" class="btn-primary">Get a Free Assessment</a>
      <a href="tel:4108584031" class="btn-ghost"><Icon name="lucide:phone" /> (410) 858-4031</a>
      <a href="mailto:info@bluecapit.com" class="btn-ghost"><Icon name="lucide:mail" /> info@bluecapit.com</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
